<media id="fs-id1430784" alt="This answer graph shows the x y-coordinate plane. The x and y-axis each run from -6 to 6. There are two labeled points: the first is ordered pair (5, 2), and the second is (2, 5)">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_BMath_Figure_11_01_008_img.jpg"/>
