</table><para id="fs-id1610522">To find a third solution, we’ll let <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> and solve for <m:math><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:math></para>

