</table><para id="fs-id1570970">We can find more solutions to the equation by substituting any value of <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> or any value of <m:math><m:mi>y</m:mi></m:math> and solving the resulting equation to get another ordered pair that is a solution. There are an infinite number of solutions for this equation.</para>
<example id="fs-id1571174">
